Create staging tables and populating the tables

In this step, we will be creating the staging Database and all the tables we need to load our source data into.   

Creating the Staging Data Base and the Staging Tables


To create the Database and all the staging tables, navigate to the extracted document you retrieved in steps 8 then navigate to the directory shown below. 

Right-click on the 01-NYC_Oil_Gas_Staging as shown below and Open with SSMS XX ( Where XX is your version number ) as shown in the image below.

Login to SSMS 


The script will be opened in the Query Editor. Click on Execute as shown below to create all the Staging Database and tables as shown below
